{
  "texts": [
    "Out of 1,894 patients, 1509 had available answers sufficient to decide if a patient was eligible or ineligible (\"Yes\" to at least one exclusion criteria question, or \"No\" to at least one exclusion criteria question and \"Yes\" or \"No\" to inclusion criteria question).",
    "Expert clinician review classified 1,162 of these patients as eligible and 347 as ineligible.",
    "We used GPT-4 Vision (Model version 1015) in this study which is referred to as GPT-4 throughout this manuscript since we only used language capabilities of the model.",
    "We identified Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) architecture 12 as a suitable solution for this study.",
    "First, we needed GPT-4 to be able to access external data, namely clinical notes of patients."
  ]
}